com.quest.glue.api.services
Annotation Type Inject

@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value={FIELD,METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR})
public @interface Inject

An annotation that can be placed on fields, methods, or constructors to indicate that the dependency injection provided by ServiceFactory should be used to provide a value for the annotated element.

When used on a constructor or method, all the parameters must be available from the dependency injection system or an exception will be triggered.

Since:
5.6.10
